**Law:** `SOURCEA_LIVE_FOUNDER_DECISION_FORM_LOCKED_v1.md` · INCIDENT-037 · `docs/SOURCEA_INCIDENT_037_FORM_FOUNDER_SUPREMACY_LOCKED_v1.md`

## Golden rule

> **FOUNDER PICK > AGENT RECOMMENDATION > DISK GATHER ROW**

## Hard rule (founder locked)

> **Only ASF clicking Submit with explicit picks writes §ANSWERED. Recommended is a hint only. Agents MUST NOT run apply/sync/submit scripts.**

## Forbidden for agents (always)

- `canvas_form_apply_picks_v1.py --apply` or `--sync-applied`
- `canvas_form_submit_v1.py`
- `hub_form_submit_v1.py` with `--actor agent` or `submit_automatic()` from CLI
- Bulk-writing §ANSWERED from recommended column
- Displaying recommended as selected answer · label `AUTOMATIC`

## Forbidden in hub form UI (`agent-control-panel/form/`)

- Copy / paste / clipboard buttons or text
- ASF batch preview boxes
- "Reply in Worker chat" instructions
- `FIVE-STEP — PICK` founder-facing copy flows
- One-question wizard (prev/next)
- Read-only automatic display · footer "automatic"
- Redesigning form UI without UI upgrade first-check

## Allowed

- **Radio per row** — founder taps A/B/C/D (or YES/NO) on each question
- **Submit my picks** → `POST /api/live-founder-decision-form-v1` with `founder_submit: true` + full `picks` map
- Server: `hub_form_submit_v1.submit_founder_picks(actor=founder)` — rejects incomplete picks
- **Recommended** shown as "Agent suggestion only (not your pick)"
- Hub page = mirror only · M1 Canvas is FORM SSOT

